Havotron looked to Apeface as he entered.  "I should have you 
killed for interrupting me, Apeface.  However" he said after a pause 
"You have provided me with good news and you yourself will go 
now and find Nightmare and Jagged.  They are invaluable to us."

Needlenose followed Spinister out of the room.  "Where to now?"
